Biography:

Conjure One is the project of ex Front Line Assembly and Delerium member Rhys Fulber augmented live by vocalist/bassist Leah Randi and on record by guests, such as vocalists Poe and Chemda. Fulber is also known for his production work with bands like Fear Factory, Paradise Lost and Mindless Self Indulgence...
